    <title><![CDATA[iOS 8 按需连接 VPN的描述文件]]></title>
    <link href="http://bao3.org/2015/08/29/iOS-8-%E6%8C%89%E9%9C%80%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5-VPN%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/"/>
    <id>http://bao3.org/2015/08/29/iOS-8-按需连接-VPN的描述文件/</id>
    <published>2015-08-29T15:26:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-08-29T17:45:48.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>适合阅读本文的人群：喜欢动手，有困难时可以查阅官方文档的 <strong><em>VPN使用者</em></strong>, 没错，不必是 VPN发行商。</p>
<p>最近在为<strong>黑帮</strong>制作一个 iPhone一个自动连接的 VPN配置文件，但发现实现起来有各种不爽，于是在网络上搜了一下。应该说全中文网没有好的共享方案，直到看到了<a href="https://maoxian.de/2014/10/setup-ikev2-on-demand-vpn-on-ios-8-and-ikev2-ikev1-cisco-ipsec-vpn-with-strongswan/1220.html" target="_blank" rel="external">maoxian.de</a> 这篇在 iOS8上实现 VPN按需连接的文章，才算是勉强通用，不过也不尽如人意。原作者的问题在于，VPN为<code>长连接状态</code>而不是真的按需连接。原本是在作者的下面提供了我的一些见解，不过与作者的实战经验有差别，所以没能显示出来。所以我想另写一篇自己的经验分享，希望中文圈可以有自己的定制。</p>
<p>这篇文章是参考了以下几章节：</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://help.apple.com/deployment/ios/#/iordfafc6ead" target="_blank" rel="external">IOS 部署参考 - Apple </a></li>
<li><a href="https://developer.apple.com/library/prerelease/mac/featuredarticles/iPhoneConfigurationProfileRef/Introduction/Introduction.html" target="_blank" rel="external">Configuration Profile Key Reference -Apple 描述文件键值定义</a></li>
<li><a href="https://maoxian.de/2014/10/setup-ikev2-on-demand-vpn-on-ios-8-and-ikev2-ikev1-cisco-ipsec-vpn-with-strongswan/1220.html" target="_blank" rel="external">Setup IKEv2 On Demand VPN on iOS - Maoxian</a></li>
<li><a href="https://wiki.strongswan.org/projects/strongswan/wiki/AppleIKEv2Profile" target="_blank" rel="external">IKEv2 Configuration Profile for Apple iOS 8 and newer - Strongswan</a></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>在接下来的这个文章中我将实现的功能：</p>
<ul>
<li>WiFi 下自动连接，关屏或者断 WiFi自动断开，目的是为了连接公共 WiFi的安全性</li>
<li>按域名，自动连接</li>
<li>长连接，无论何时永远连接 VPN</li>
</ul>
<p>显然以上三个目标是无法在一个VPN下面达成，不过我们可以多一个心眼 —— 多创建几个同样的 VPN，例如我创建的是<code>IKEv2-WiFi</code> ， <code>IKEv2-Domain</code> ，<code>IKEv2-Alaways</code> ，虽然这在 iOS上会显示成 3个不同的 VPN名字，但其实是同一个 VPN，只是功能不同，适合不同的人群需求。</p>
<h1 id="WiFi下自动连接_VPN">WiFi下自动连接 VPN</h1><p>在苹果给出的开发手册上主要能实现的功能是<code>判断 SSID</code> 来决定连接或者不连接，或者所有 WiFi下都连接 VPN，甚至是在 SSID下测试某个 URL能否成功来决定是不是要连接 VPN。对于我们普通人而言，基本是在所有 WiFi下都自动连接最简单。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>对于越狱并且使用 Shadowsocks的朋友来说</em>，非常推荐使用  <code>在所有 WiFi下都自动连接VPN</code> </p>
</blockquote>
<p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">            &lt;!-- Setup WiFi --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandEnabled<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandRules<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 这个故意保留，您可以自定在哪些WiFi不必自动连接或连接</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dict&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;key&gt;Action&lt;/key&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;string&gt;Disconnect&lt;/string&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;key&gt;InterfaceTypeMatch&lt;/key&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;string&gt;WiFi&lt;/string&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;key&gt;SSIDMatch&lt;/key&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;array&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Coco_baobao-5G<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 接下来这部分是规定了在 WiFi下自动连接Ikev2 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Connect<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>InterfaceTypeMatch<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>WiFi<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 下面的 Cellular则是要求手机在3G/4G下不自动 VPN --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Disconnect<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>InterfaceTypeMatch<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Cellular<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!--以上就是自动 WiFi连接的设定 --&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</p>
<p>是不是觉得很简单？代码中的注释，你可以不用删除，因为导入手机或者 <code>Apple Configurator</code> 之后自动就过滤掉了。<br><strong>那么问题来了，代码要插入到哪里？</strong>其实很简单，根据官方手册，只要插入到 VPN协商配置那一段就可以，这里我以 IKEv2的配置为例，入位置如下：<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;dict&gt; <span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 请注意这第一个 dict --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>AuthName<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>ios8<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>AuthPassword<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Demo@iOS<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>AuthenticationMethod<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>SharedSecret<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>ChildSecurityAssociationParameters<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>DiffieHellmanGroup<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>EncryptionAlgorithm<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>3DES<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>IntegrityAlgorithm<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>SHA1-96<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>LifeTimeInMinutes<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1440<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>DeadPeerDetectionRate<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Low<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>ExtendedAuthEnabled<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">true</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>IKESecurityAssociationParameters<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>DiffieHellmanGroup<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>EncryptionAlgorithm<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>3DES<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>IntegrityAlgorithm<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>SHA1-96<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>LifeTimeInMinutes<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1440<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>LocalIdentifier<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>vpn.googday.club<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>RemoteAddress<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>vpn.googday.club<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>RemoteIdentifier<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>vpn.googday.club<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>SharedSecret<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>googday<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 开始按需定制 WiFi连接 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandEnabled<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandRules<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 这个故意保留，您可以自定在哪些WiFi不必自动连接</span><br><span class="line">         &lt;dict&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;key&gt;Action&lt;/key&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;string&gt;Disconnect&lt;/string&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;key&gt;InterfaceTypeMatch&lt;/key&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;string&gt;WiFi&lt;/string&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;key&gt;SSIDMatch&lt;/key&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;array&gt;</span><br><span class="line">				&lt;string&gt;Coco_baobao-5G&lt;/string&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;/array&gt;</span><br><span class="line">       &lt;/dict&gt;</span><br><span class="line">       --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 接下来这部分是规定了在 WiFi下自动连接Ikev2 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Connect<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>InterfaceTypeMatch<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>WiFi<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 下面的 Cellular则是要求手机在3G/4G下不自动 VPN --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Disconnect<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>InterfaceTypeMatch<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Cellular<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">&lt;!--以上就是自动 WiFi连接的设定 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 注意这个dict ，请把代码插入这个中间的位置 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>IPv4<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OverridePrimary<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>PayloadDescription<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Configures VPN settings<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>PayloadDisplayName<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>VPN<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>怎么样，其实没有想象中的难吧，这样一来，你就可以将你所买到的 VPN供应商的描述文件自己动手改造一下咯。下面的部分我就不再这样重复了，因为要插入的位置是一样的。</p>
<h1 id="按域名自动连接">按域名自动连接</h1><p>按域名的实现，很多前辈在 iOS 7以前的时代就实现过，不过很不幸 iOS 8有一些改变，有些字段不太一样了，所以我才要自己研究一下。不多说，功能就是按照域名列表来实现自动连接。<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- 加入自己想要的域名 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandEnabled<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandRules<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>EvaluateConnection<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>ActionParameters<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>DomainAction<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>ConnectIfNeeded<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Domains<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 加入自己想要的域名 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*twitter.com<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*dropbox.com<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*google.com<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*google.co.jp<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*facebook.com<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*youtube.com<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>*instagram.com<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">					<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>t.co<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="长连接">长连接</h1><p>也有人喜欢让自己的 VPN一直连着，那么只要加入下面这条就直接可以实现了：<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">     &lt;!-- 开始按需定制 WiFi连接 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandEnabled<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>OnDemandRules<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span>Connect<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">dict</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">arry</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="可否将这几种配置合成使用？">可否将这几种配置合成使用？</h1><p>我也是这么想的，不过这涉及很混乱的逻辑以及判断性能，只能说， WiFi自动连接与按域名自动连接目前还没有很好的共存且共同起作用。我还在继续测试，目前我的解决方案就是前面提到的同一个VPN建三份，然后配上不同的配置，根据需要选定其中一个满足不同的人。就我个人来说，我只是使用 WiFi下自动连接 ，记住任何免费WiFi都有可能是蜜罐，用来入侵你的设备。</p>
<p>文章先写到这里。 有空再补充<br><em>完结</em></p>
]]></content>
